    • Uses of CallbackUrlResolver in org.pac4j.core.http.callback

      Classes in org.pac4j.core.http.callback that implement CallbackUrlResolver 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      class  NoParameterCallbackUrlResolver
      No name is added to the callback URL to be able to distinguish the client, so it doesn't match.
      class  PathParameterCallbackUrlResolver
      The client name is added to the path of the callback URL.
      class  QueryParameterCallbackUrlResolver
      The client name is added as a query parameter to the callback URL.
